Author: snorux, KangasZ, BumbleBeever
Name: Eureka Helper
Punchline: Eureka Tracker in a plugin with QoL features.
Description:
A tool to assist you on your Eureka adventures. Type /eurekahelper to get started.

Features include:
- In-Game Tracker GUI
- Instance Tracker
- Elementals Tracker
- Relic Helper
- Alarms
-Money NM weather timings
- More to come

Refactored for DT by KangasZ.
Packaged and added to a temp repo.

This release is for testing purposes ONLY.
For updates refer to: https://github.com/snorux/EurekaHelper
